{"tid":1329333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個仲未放棄既原因","createTime":"2019-07-18T07:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T13:06:58.000Z","uid":60539,"like":147,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"549d7879df3803d08890c6b26e13735e171e049e","tid":1329333,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"作為一個90後<br />\n英治 回歸 廿三條 沙士<br />\n呢個大概就係我既童年<br />\n當時既我乜都唔知唔識 <br />\n淨係識食識玩<br />\n第一次政治干涉到我既身活我諗就係領滙<br />\n我由細食到大既茶餐廳 快餐店 文具舖 雜貨店<br />\n一間一間因為加租而結業<br />\n仲記得每次去食野<br />\n啲老闆 伙記永遠都會同你寒暄幾句<br />\n&quot;冬0茶少甜少冰係咪？&quot;<br />\n&quot;今日唔洗返學阿？&quot;<br />\n&quot;女朋友阿？幾靚喎&quot;<br />\n呢種人情味係集團式既食店已經揾唔返<br />\n第一次覺得原來幾年前既一個政策<br />\n影響咁深遠<br />\n到反國教 928 佔中<br />\n我已經有自己獨立既思想<br />\n係我第一次企出黎爭取自己既將來<br />\n果種感覺好實在<br />\n唔係唱k睇戲食飯比到你既感覺<br />\n為自己既將來拼搏 係唔會怕辛苦<br />\n可惜既係運動失敗<br />\n但喚醒左港獨 本土意識<br />\n開始有本土派既人參選<br />\n於是我登記做左選民<br />\n但無奈既係政府可以不擇手段咁將我地既代表一個一個DQ<br />\n我地仲有咩可以做到？<br />\n果一刻好悲憤 好絕望<br />\n開始計劃移民<br />\n亦有朋友已經去左唔同既地方生活<br />\n但係佢地口中得知<br />\n移民其實唔係想像中咁幸福<br />\n同一個文化背景 用同一堆潮語 講一樣既粗口<br />\n同聲同氣既人 原來係好珍貴<br />\n果種sense of belonging 係令人好安心<br />\n就係咁一直處於一個兩難既局面<br />\n留低乜都做唔到 離開乜都從頭黎過<br />\n好無力好困惑好迷惘<br />\n一直無希望咁行落去<br />\n抑鬱成為身邊每個人都有既病 唔再罕有<br />\n有人自殺唔再覺得可惜反而佩服佢地既勇氣<br />\n直至69<br />\n見到咁多人仲未放棄<br />\n我開始諗<br />\n點解我既屋企我無得話事？<br />\n你班人想點就點有無問過我？<br />\n我仲有咩可以輸<br />\n坐監咪坐監囉<br />\n到時入到去應該有好多同路人陪我<br />\n有案底咪有案底<br />\n當呢個社會個個都有案底<br />\n咁一個案底代表到啲咩？<br />\n我寧願入去坐 真真正正無自由<br />\n好過對住虛偽既假自由感恩<br />\n我寧願盡力而失敗 問心無愧<br />\n好過後悔自己無企出黎<br />\n每次企出黎 都覺得自己原來唔孤獨<br />\n大家守望相助 好有人情味 好有安全感 <br />\n好想守護呢一班人<br />\n好想香港以後就係咁團結<br />\n第一次對香港咁有歸屬感<br />\n生係香港人 死係香港魂<br />\ntear gas 胡椒 橡膠彈 水炮 實彈有咩好怕<br />\n我最怕係香港既靈魂從此消失<br />\n最怕以後再揾唔返呢種歸屬感<br />\n講到尾都係得一個原因<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我好愛香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e27d028ea78fffd6ff2951dd151c6d3475836c31","tid":1329333,"uid":257422,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"突發！！！！ ]  荷蘭首都大學、意大利米蘭街頭 分別驚見 林鄭壽終正寢 街招！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329216</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">荷蘭</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/nNQk9Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNQk9Fe.jpg&h=5971b37f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">意大利</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67260952_2334870509933092_2471868942885322752_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkOaykJcWH9Wa5gUItjj08X6dcp8r3HK5_qNCEeSXnxjg_dHKav3hwm2FiACInNlK8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg8-1.fna&amp;oh=a1c45d97e8e22774df7d25b943c4a7dc&amp;oe=5DECEFD7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67260952_2334870509933092_2471868942885322752_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkOaykJcWH9Wa5gUItjj08X6dcp8r3HK5_qNCEeSXnxjg_dHKav3hwm2FiACInNlK8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg8-1.fna%26oh%3Da1c45d97e8e22774df7d25b943c4a7dc%26oe%3D5DECEFD7&h=56d1a4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://serving.photos.photobox.com/928067831b471809fec84560cf12f81a4d43a939e63327e60d44b8c434697b1bd6e14a35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fserving.photos.photobox.com%2F928067831b471809fec84560cf12f81a4d43a939e63327e60d44b8c434697b1bd6e14a35.jpg&h=23c7c688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">個QR code會link去下面條片</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6_RdnVtfZPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6_RdnVtfZPY&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=c32861ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6_RdnVtfZPY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">海外手足 / 準備去旅行既 print定幫手貼</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9352d304c4f9d3ad91a2f8d9f066d03f3fdeb3ee","tid":1329333,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"因為場波未打完"},{"pid":"6f317b342e3caf933e72c0fdb25fde250c2eedf4","tid":1329333,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"想知大家既諗法"},{"pid":"9f1c4c5aac0aa77fc75b2af8e6d586ea7bdcfa41","tid":1329333,"uid":60539,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9352d304c4f9d3ad91a2f8d9f066d03f3fdeb3ee","tid":1329333,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"因為場波未打完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"開頭以為打既係政策<br />\n但慢慢發現<br />\n我地打緊既已經係final boss<br />\n你有無心理準備呢場波會打好幾年"},{"pid":"556a123b59776d92c5d603eedfd04cba8279005d","tid":1329333,"uid":240890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9f1c4c5aac0aa77fc75b2af8e6d586ea7bdcfa41","tid":1329333,"uid":60539,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9352d304c4f9d3ad91a2f8d9f066d03f3fdeb3ee","tid":1329333,"uid"